OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Asia Correspondent
OL,7,FDebi Edward and Sanjay Jha, ITV News
OL,8,Fin New Delhi.
OL,10,FTanvi is proud to call herself a
OL,11,F'cockroach'.
OL,13,FShe's one of the millions of young
OL,14,Fpeople across India that has joined
OL,15,Fthe protest launched by the Cockroach
OL,16,FJanata Party, who say they are
OL,17,Ffighting for a better future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
