PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784789276
OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FThe party's name comes from an insult
OL,7,Faimed at the country's unemployed
OL,8,Fyouth, that was reclaimed by India's
OL,9,FGen Z to symbolise their resistance.
OL,11,FTanvi, 21, is a sociology masters
OL,12,Fstudent, and spoke to us after being
OL,13,Ftreated for injuries she sustained
OL,14,Fduring violent clashes between police
OL,15,Fand protesters in Delhi.
OL,17,FShe was in a wheelchair, unable to
OL,18,Fwalk, with bandages on her arm and
OL,19,Fbruising on her chest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
