OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FShe told us that as the crowd swelled,
OL,7,Fthe police grew increasingly
OL,8,Faggressive, before they suddenly
OL,9,Fsurged with no warning, wielding
OL,10,Fsticks and firing tear gas.
OL,12,FThe result was chaos. Thousands of
OL,13,Fpeople running in all directions, many
OL,14,Ftripping over and falling prey to the
OL,15,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
