OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,F"We were pushed towards a large iron
OL,7,Frailing with barbed wire. There were
OL,8,Fseveral female students standing
OL,9,Fthere, shouting and crying, pleading
OL,10,Fwith the police to stop because they
OL,11,Fwere hitting them with their lathis
OL,12,F(bamboo sticks)," Tanvi said.
OL,14,FTanvi couldn't believe how violent it
OL,15,Fbecame in such a short space of time.
OL,16,FAs she managed to escape with her
OL,17,Ffriends, she said she could see blood
OL,18,Frunning down the road.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
