OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FWhen they reached the RML hospital, it
OL,7,Fwas crowded with injured protesters,
OL,8,Fso they went home to nurse their
OL,9,Fwounds instead.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FBut by nighttime, Tanvi's condition
OL,17,Fhad worsened, and they rushed her to
OL,18,Fanother hospital nearby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
