OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784789276
OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FThe Cockroach movement began in May
OL,7,Ffollowing a leak of national exam
OL,8,Fpapers, affecting more than two
OL,9,Fmillion students, and requiring them
OL,10,Fto re-sit the exam.
OL,12,FIt wasn't the first time that exam
OL,13,Fpapers or results had been leaked, or
OL,14,Fthat the Indian education department
OL,15,Fhad faced accusations of cheating or
OL,16,Fcorruption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
