FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784789276
OL,3,CIndia's bruised and battered Cockroach
OL,4,Cprotesters vow to continue fight
OL,6,FAt first, protestors demanded the
OL,7,Fresignation of the country's education
OL,8,Fminister, Dharmendra Pradhan, a demand
OL,9,Fwhich quickly amassed the support of
OL,10,Fmillions online.
OL,12,FDespite recent examples in Nepal and
OL,13,FBangladesh, it appears that the Indian
OL,14,Fgovernment underestimated the
OL,15,Fpotential for that digital dissent to
OL,16,Ftransform into mass demonstrations.
OL,18,FIn Delhi, Tanvi and her friends may be
OL,19,Fbruised and battered, but they say
OL,20,Fthey remain determined to continue
OL,21,Fwith their fight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
